{"tid":629789,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"凌文龍佛系爭獎","createTime":"2018-04-15T04:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T04:08:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fb7342ef9523dcd1588c97beea0f744282d54b83","tid":629789,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:08:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180415/20361765?_ga=2.39954082.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F20361765%3F_ga%3D2.39954082.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=e2PC5uQKZy0AmFTAHjyWpu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=4900ab73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F20361765%3F_ga%3D2.39954082.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=5021b1a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180415/20361765?_ga=2.39954082.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n凌文龍佛系爭獎<br />\n<br />\n2.8K<br />\n娛樂名人<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180415/large/15ec6p13e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180415%2Flarge%2F15ec6p13e.jpg&h=ab282dbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n凌文龍童年甚少睇戲，笑言因此對表演感興趣。<br />\n<br />\n今年電影圈新人輩出，早有梁雍婷被張經緯發掘在《藍天白雲》演弒母角色，後有凌文龍在《黃金花》中演自閉症人士。凌文龍自演藝學院戲劇學院畢業後，便投身香港話劇團成為全職演員，首部電影就為他帶來金像獎「最佳男主角」及「新演員」兩項提名，他以「佛系」概念說：「都係機緣，有次毛姐睇過我做舞台劇，部戲開時就諗起我。」<br />\n<br />\n《黃》片首日在街市開工，嘈雜外，工作人員都非常忙，導演忽然就叫埋位，凌文龍感謝余安安，他說：「佢哋好忙唔敢問，但唔問就開始，多得安安姐跟場照顧我，佢話畀我聽邊度做得太緊。到第二、三日就習慣。」凌文龍自言兒時家教嚴以及家境問題，甚少接觸電視和電影，他說：「好多劇同電影都冇得睇，會偷睇，不過爸爸返嚟一摸部機熱唔熱，就知有冇開過。」他笑言可能因此令自己對表演感到好奇。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：何永寧、Sapna<br />\n攝影：Neo<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180415/large/15ec6p14e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180415%2Flarge%2F15ec6p14e.jpg&h=cf494077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《黃金花》是凌文龍（左）首部電影作品。劇照<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n娜姐攞獎死而無憾<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n毛舜筠了解對手<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n鄭中基若封帝感謝太太<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n被毛舜筠演技震撼視為勁敵Stephy爭影后：未識得緊張<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晚 2000-2330 第37屆香港電影金像獎頒獎典禮 ViuTV 99台 (4月15日 星期日)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/629720/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/629720/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}